title: What You Must Do To Become Elite With Justin Stenstrom
itunes:title: What You Must Do To Become Elite With Justin Stenstrom
description:
Everybody says they want to be great, but few back that up with their actions.
 
If you want to make it to the top and be elite, then you better be ready work your face off.
 
Justin Stenstrom the host of the Elite Man Podcast, a top-rated podcast on iTunes.
 
In this interview, we went deep on what it really means to be elite and how you can put yourself in a class by yourself, above all the wannabes.
 
Show Notes: https://underdogempowerment.com/justin-stenstrom/
